/node_modules
/.next
.env.local
npm-debug.log*

# NOTE: /out (the static build) is intentionally NOT ignored.
# `databricks sync` skips .gitignored paths, and the deployed app must include
# the built frontend. Build it (npm run build) before deploying. You may either
# commit /out or leave it untracked — both get synced as long as it's not ignored.
